data.description: Indulge in the ultimate luxury living experience within this meticulously crafted 4-bedroom, 2-full bath masterpiece. No detail has been overlooked in the custom remodeling, highlighting exquisite features like hardwood floors, designer carpets, and custom-tiled baths. Step into the ideal setting for hosting unforgettable gatherings with a seamlessly designed open floor plan. This complete openness welcomes you as you enter, creating the perfect ambiance for entertaining. Whether it's a social gathering or a cozy get-together, this thoughtfully designed space ensures a dynamic and inviting atmosphere for all your hosting needs. Elevate your entertaining experience in a home that effortlessly combines style and functionality. Revel in the convenience of both a 2-car attached and a 2-car detached garage, complete with a half bathroom. A freshly paved driveway and a delightful maintenance-free front porch add to the allure, making this home a flawless fusion of style and practicality. Seize the opportunity to immerse yourself in the sophistication and comfort that grace every corner of this residence.
